                    <span class="badge badge-secondary">Regular Member</span>
                  </td>
                  <td>Apr 2020</td>
                  <td>
                    <a href="tel:+254704567890" class="link">Call</a> •
                    <a href="mailto:alice@example.com" class="link">Email</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <p class="small" style="margin-top: 15px">
              Showing 5 of 22 members. <a href="#" class="link">View all</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- GROUP BYLAWS & RULES -->
        <section class="dashboard-section">
          <h2 class="h2">Group Bylaws & Rules</h2>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button
                  class="accordion-header"
                  onclick="toggleAccordion(this)"
                >
                  <strong>Membership Requirements</strong>
                  <span>+</span>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" style="display: none">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <h5>Eligibility Criteria:</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0">
                      <li>✓ Must be 18 years or older</li>
                      <li>✓ Must reside in the community</li>
                      <li>✓ Must have a valid national ID</li>
                      <li>✓ Must pay application fee of KES 500</li>
                      <li>
                        ✓ Must commit to monthly contributions of KES 5,000
                      </li>
                      <li>✓ Must attend at least 80% of meetings</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button
                  class="accordion-header"
                  onclick="toggleAccordion(this)"
                >
                  <strong>Contribution Policies</strong>
                  <span>+</span>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" style="display: none">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <h5>Contribution Rules:</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0">
                      <li>✓ Minimum contribution: KES 5,000 per month</li>
                      <li>
                        ✓ Payment must be made by the last Friday of each month
                      </li>
                      <li>✓ Late payment penalty: 2% per week</li>
                      <li>
                        ✓ Accepted payment methods: M-Pesa, Bank Transfer, Cash
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        ✓ Contributions are non-refundable except for loan
                        defaults
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button
                  class="accordion-header"
                  onclick="toggleAccordion(this)"
                >
                  <strong>Loan Policy</strong>
                  <span>+</span>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" style="display: none">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <h5>Loan Terms:</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0">
                      <li>
                        ✓ Maximum loan amount: 3x monthly contributions (KES
                        15,000)
                      </li>
                      <li>✓ Interest rate: 5% per annum</li>
                      <li>✓ Repayment period: 3-24 months</li>
                      <li>✓ Processing fee: KES 500 per application</li>
                      <li>
                        ✓ Loan approval: Requires committee review (7-10 days)
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        ✓ Late payment penalty: 1% per week on outstanding
                        balance
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button
                  class="accordion-header"
                  onclick="toggleAccordion(this)"
                >
                  <strong>Meeting Conduct</strong>
                  <span>+</span>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" style="display: none">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <h5>Meeting Rules:</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0">
                      <li>
                        ✓ General meetings held on last Friday of each month
                      </li>
                      <li>✓ Minimum quorum: 50% of members</li>
                      <li>✓ Meeting starts at 6:00 PM sharp</li>
                      <li>✓ All members have equal voting rights</li>
                      <li>✓ Decisions made by majority vote</li>
                      <li>✓ Meeting minutes recorded and distributed</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button
                  class="accordion-header"
                  onclick="toggleAccordion(this)"
                >
                  <strong>Code of Conduct</strong>
                  <span>+</span>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" style="display: none">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <h5>Expected Behavior:</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0">
                      <li>✓ Maintain honesty and integrity in all dealings</li>
                      <li>✓ Respect and support fellow members</li>
                      <li>✓ Participate actively in group activities</li>
                      <li>✓ Keep confidential information private</li>
                      <li>✓ Maintain professional conduct at all times</li>
                      <li>
                        ✓ Breach of conduct may result in suspension or
                        expulsion
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- DOWNLOAD DOCUMENTS -->
        <section class="dashboard-section">
          <h2 class="h2">Important Documents</h2>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="document-list">
              <div class="document-item">
                <strong>Group Constitution</strong>
                <p class="small">Last updated: January 15, 2025</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-small btn-ghost">Download PDF</a>
              </div>
              <hr style="margin: 15px 0" />
              <div class="document-item">
                <strong>Financial Policies</strong>
                <p class="small">Last updated: December 1, 2024</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-small btn-ghost">Download PDF</a>
              </div>
              <hr style="margin: 15px 0" />
              <div class="document-item">
                <strong>Loan Agreement Template</strong>
                <p class="small">Last updated: November 10, 2024</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-small btn-ghost">Download PDF</a>
              </div>
              <hr style="margin: 15px 0" />
              <div class="document-item">
                <strong>Annual Financial Report 2025</strong>
                <p class="small">Published: January 20, 2026</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-small btn-ghost">Download PDF</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px">
          <a href="/member/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary"
            >Back to Dashboard</a
          >
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <script>
      function toggleAccordion(header) {
        const content = header.nextElementSibling;
        const isOpen = content.style.display !== "none";

        // Close all other accordion items
        document.querySelectorAll(".accordion-content").forEach((item) => {
          item.style.display = "none";
        });
        document.querySelectorAll(".accordion-header span").forEach((span) => {
          span.textContent = "+";
        });

        // Toggle current item
        if (!isOpen) {
          content.style.display = "block";
          header.querySelector("span").textContent = "−";
        }
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
